<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doctor Profile</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Light gray background */
            color: #333; /* Dark gray text */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px; /* Limit the width of the profile */
            margin: 50px auto; /* Center the container */
            padding: 30px; /* Increased padding for a spacious look */
            background: white; /* White background for the profile */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Enhanced shadow */
            text-align: center; /* Center text */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #007bff; /* Blue color for the heading */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space below the heading */
            font-size: 28px; /* Font size for heading */
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px; /* Font size for the paragraph */
            line-height: 1.6; /* Line height for better readability */
            margin-bottom: 30px; /* Space below the paragraph */
        }

        .profile-card {
            background: #e9ecef; /* Light background for the profile card */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space below the card */
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow */
        }

        .logout-button {
            padding: 10px 20px; /* Padding for the button */
            background-color: #dc3545; /* Red background for logout */
            color: white; /* White text */
            border: none; /* Remove default border */
            border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded corners for the button */
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline from the link */
            font-size: 16px; /* Larger text */
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s; /* Smooth transition for background color and scaling */
            cursor: pointer; /* Cursor pointer for better UX */
        }

        .logout-button:hover {
            background-color: #c82333; /* Darker red on hover */
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Scale up on hover */
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px; /* Space above the footer */
            font-size: 14px; /* Smaller font for footer */
            color: #666; /* Gray color for footer text */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome, <%= doctor.email %></h1>
        <div class="profile-card">
            <p>Great to have you here! ðŸ˜Š</p>
            <p>Your role as a doctor is crucial in helping patients achieve better health. Keep up the great work!</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/doctors/logout" class="logout-button">Logout</a>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2024 Telehealth. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
